STRING 4223
// Items: IL70 (WC2HumanAct01Terenas15), Description (Description)
{
We the kings of the Alliance do hereby appoint Lord Anduin Lothar, Champion of Azeroth, as our Supreme Commander!
}

STRING 4224
// Items: IL70 (WC2HumanAct01Terenas15), Name (Name)
{
WC2HumanAct01Terenas15
}

STRING 4226
// Items: IL71 (WC2HumanAct01Thoras01), Description (Description)
{
Orcs? Are they some kind of trolls? And where did this horde come from? As far as I know, you have dealt with the trolls of the southern jungles before.
}

STRING 4227
// Items: IL71 (WC2HumanAct01Thoras01), Name (Name)
{
WC2HumanAct01Thoras01
