STRING 4232
// Items: IL73 (WC2HumanAct01Thoras03), Description (Description)
{
On that I agree Sir Lothar. However, if we are to establish this union, I only see fit that I lead it to battle!
}

STRING 4233
// Items: IL73 (WC2HumanAct01Thoras03), Name (Name)
{
WC2HumanAct01Thoras03
}

STRING 4236
// Items: IL74 (WC2HumanAct01Thoras04), Name (Name)
{
WC2HumanAct01Thoras04
}

STRING 4237
// Items: IL09 (WC2HumanAct01Danath02), Description (Description)
{
I admit that is a wise choice, but Lordaeron and Dalaran require our help right now.
}

STRING 4241
// Items: IL25 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar06), Description (Description)
{
You will take charge of settling our people in this region. Make sure everything is in order until we return.
}

STRING 4242
// Items: IL28 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar09), Description (Description)
{
Your Majesties, I thank you for attending this meeting, and for listening to what I have to say. I am no poet or diplomat but a warrior, so I will keep my words brief and blunt. I must tell you that my home, Stormwind, is no more.
}

STRING 4246
// Items: IL37 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar18), Description (Description)
{
Yes, but we have lost Stromgarde, Tol Barad, Stratholme and much, much more…
}

STRING 4247
// Items: IL38 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar19), Description (Description)
{
But this is no time to ponder. Willhelm, travel north, reach Commander Turalyon. It’s imperative he reinforces the capital’s defenses as soon as possible.
}

STRING 4249
// Items: IL47 (WC2HumanAct01Meryn02), Description (Description)
{
I will do my best, Lord Lothar.
}

STRING 4250
// Items: IL62 (WC2HumanAct01Terenas07), Description (Description)
{
I present to you Anduin Lothar, Champion of Stormwind. He has come here as a messenger. I think it best if I let him tell you himself what he has seen and what we may soon expect ourselves.
}

STRING 4251
// Items: IL65 (WC2HumanAct01Terenas10), Description (Description)
{
Do I need to remind at whose behest are we here? Who sponsored this council from the beginning? We need more than a mere battle commander, we need someone who can unite us.
}

STRING 4253
// Items: IL74 (WC2HumanAct01Thoras04), Description (Description)
{
And his bloodline. My ancestors fought beside Thoradin before, it would be a great honor to do so again by following his descendant.
}

