STRING 4322
// Items: IL22 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar03), Description (Description)
{
Stormwind...
}

STRING 4323
{
Three years of bloody war have devastated the Eastern Kingdoms. Ironforge is under siege, the forests of Quel'Thalas burn with dragonfire, and countless cities lie in ruins.
}

STRING 4327
{
Kul Tiran and Gilnean forces remain isolated in their coastal enclaves. The capitals of Lordaeron and Dalaran are besieged by the Horde.
}

STRING 4328
{
Meanwhile, Anduin Lothar gathers his forces in Andorhal, rallying after a fierce battle with orcish raiders…
}

STRING 4329
// Units: HLPA (Supreme Commander), Propernames (Proper Names)
{
Sir Anduin Lothar
}

STRING 4330
// Units: HLPA (Supreme Commander), Name (Name)
{
Supreme Commander
}

STRING 4331
// Units: HLPA (Supreme Commander), EditorSuffix (Name - Editor Suffix)
{
(Cinematic No Glow Pre Alliance)
}

STRING 4332
// Items: IL17 (WC2HumanAct01Khadgar01), Description (Description)
{
Indeed. The township of Soutshore, between Dalaran and Alterac.
}

STRING 4334
// Items: IL72 (WC2HumanAct01Thoras02), Description (Description)
{
What bureaucratic nonsense, Aiden! If you can't take responsibility, then leave it to those who can.
}

STRING 4335
// Items: IL49 (WC2HumanAct01Perenolde02), Description (Description)
{
I admit that the situation is serious, but I need to consult with my lawmakers and ministers before I can subscribe to any kind of war. This is how things are done in civilized kingdoms.
}

STRING 4336
// Items: IL01 (WC2HumanAct01Alonsus01), Description (Description)
{
I see where you are going…If I may, great leaders. When Northshire was decimated by the foul magic of orcish warlocks, we despaired. And when King Llane fell and Stormwind burned, we lost all hope.
}

STRING 4337
// Items: IL19 (WC2HumanAct01Khadgar03), Description (Description)
{
No trolls, Your Grace. They are an alien race, who have invaded our lands through a magical rift hidden somewhere within the southern fringes of the Black Morass.
}

STRING 4338
// Items: IL30 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar11), Description (Description)
{
Know this — the Horde will not stop at Stormwind. They mean to claim the entire world, and they have the might and the numbers to do so. Nor do they lack magical powers.
}

STRING 4339
// Items: IL36 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar17), Description (Description)
{
I just received a message that the Cross Island has fallen. It means that the Horde has reached Lordamere Lake. Seems like Alterac forces cannot defend their borders anymore… Since the beginning of this war, fortune has been against us.
}

STRING 4340
// Items: IL40 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar21), Description (Description)
{
We will secure Hillsbrad and cut orcish supply lines from the sea. Then we will hit Doomhammer’s army from the rear.
}

STRING 4341
// Items: IL68 (WC2HumanAct01Terenas13), Description (Description)
{
Now then, we have all agreed that time is of the essence if we are to marshal our united forces and meet the Horde when it arrives.
}

STRING 4342
// Items: IL69 (WC2HumanAct01Terenas14), Description (Description)
{
Then I hereby declare the founding of the Grand Alliance of Lordaeron!
}

STRING 4343
// Items: IL75 (WC2HumanAct01Khadgar03A), Tip (Tooltip - Basic)
{
Khadgar
}

STRING 4344
// Items: IL75 (WC2HumanAct01Khadgar03A), Description (Description)
{
They are terrible foes, as tall as a man and far stronger, with bestial features, green skin, and red eyes.
}

STRING 4345
// Items: IL75 (WC2HumanAct01Khadgar03A), Name (Name)
{
WC2HumanAct01Khadgar03A
}

STRING 4346
// Items: IL76 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar11A), Tip (Tooltip - Basic)
{
Anduin Lothar
}

STRING 4347
// Items: IL76 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar11A), Description (Description)
{
Once they have finished with my homeland, they will find a way to cross the ocean and come for the rest of you.
}

STRING 4348
// Items: IL76 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar11A), Name (Name)
{
WC2HumanAct01Lothar11A
}

STRING 4349
// Items: IL77 (WC2HumanAct01Alonsus01A), Tip (Tooltip - Basic)
{
Alonsus Faol
}

STRING 4350
// Items: IL77 (WC2HumanAct01Alonsus01A), Description (Description)
{
Yet there was one man who rallied us and led us through darkness. Anduin Lothar.
}

STRING 4351
// Items: IL77 (WC2HumanAct01Alonsus01A), Name (Name)
{
WC2HumanAct01Alonsus01A
}

STRING 4352
// Items: IL78 (WC2HumanAct01Terenas14A), Tip (Tooltip - Basic)
{
Terenas Menethil
}

STRING 4353
// Items: IL78 (WC2HumanAct01Terenas14A), Description (Description)
{
We shall stand together as one, as our ancestors did long ago, in the Arathi Empire. And it is only fitting, then, that our commander should hail from that ancient ruling stock.
}

STRING 4354
// Items: IL78 (WC2HumanAct01Terenas14A), Name (Name)
{
WC2HumanAct01Terenas14A
}

STRING 4355
// Items: IL79 (WC2HumanAct01Terenas13A), Tip (Tooltip - Basic)
{
Terenas Menethil
}

STRING 4356
// Items: IL79 (WC2HumanAct01Terenas13A), Description (Description)
{
Do we also agree upon our course of action?
}

STRING 4357
// Items: IL79 (WC2HumanAct01Terenas13A), Name (Name)
{
WC2HumanAct01Terenas13A
}

STRING 4358
// Items: IL80 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar17A), Tip (Tooltip - Basic)
{
Anduin Lothar
}

STRING 4359
// Items: IL80 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar17A), Description (Description)
{
We have been chasing Doomhammer across the continent, never to arrive in time… 
}

STRING 4360
// Items: IL80 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar17A), Name (Name)
{
WC2HumanAct01Lothar17A
}

STRING 4361
// Items: IL81 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar21A), Tip (Tooltip - Basic)
{
Anduin Lothar
}

STRING 4362
// Items: IL81 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar21A), Description (Description)
{
This time, we will not play his game. Instead of chasing him, we’ll place a noose around the neck of his blasted Horde… and hang them with it.
}

STRING 4363
// Items: IL81 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar21A), Name (Name)
{
WC2HumanAct01Lothar21A
}

STRING 4364
// Items: IL20 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar01), Description (Description)
{
A proper landing site…. Are we in Lordaeron?
}

STRING 4365
// Items: IL42 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar23), Description (Description)
{
Gavinrad. You will travel south with Captain Danath and provide support to his forces. After that, you will remain there and oversee the region in case the Horde attempts to flee east through Alterac. If you spot them - show no mercy.
}

STRING 4366
// Items: IL35 (WC2HumanAct01Lothar16), Description (Description)
{
This is great honor for me. I accept this charge. With your aid, noble kings, we will vanquish the Horde and spare your people from the gruesome fate of Stormwind!
}

STRING 4367
// Items: IL05 (WC2HumanAct01DaelinProudmoore01), Description (Description)
{
You say they are coming here. Do they have ships?
}

